11:03.440 --> 11:08.440
And it sort of hues around two significant losses in my life.

11:08.440 --> 11:14.440
The first was my father, who died in a reckless accident, a careless violent accident.

11:14.440 --> 11:17.440
And then 40 years later, my husband hung himself.

11:17.440 --> 11:23.440
