11:58.440 --> 12:02.440
And I actually don't think it's shameful to say, as a father of daughters, I get feminism.

12:02.440 --> 12:06.440
Because I think when we encounter people in human relationships, that's how our empathy deepens.

12:06.440 --> 12:13.440
But as a mother of a son, I see the way the education system actually problematises young male

12:13.440 --> 12:19.440
who develop more slowly, generally, and can't sit still and need to run around in general.

12:19.440 --> 12:26.440
And actually the discipline system in schools is problematising masculinity at that age.

12:26.440 --> 12:32.440
The first thing that sprung to my mind was the image of Yin Yang and the movement of one into the other.

12:32.440 --> 12:36.440
