12:45.440 --> 12:52.440
And that, I suppose, to one extent, if you kind of get it back here into balance

12:52.440 --> 12:58.440
and remove the extreme masculinity, the thing that you used to call feminine has its kind of masculine side.

12:58.440 --> 13:06.440
Just with that, I want men to be men and I know that my power is as a female in the feminine.

13:06.440 --> 13:10.440
